name: Continent of Dairon
description: The continent of Dairon, which consists of 12 countries. Dairon is one of 5 continents on the planet of Tez. The continent of Dairon is known for its volcanos and its jungles. There are four distinctive races that live on this continent. They are the Katarikian peoples, Epselium peoples, Centce peoples, and the Arix peoples. ((Zoom in!)) 3096x1548
